
'''Speciose Ayinkamiye''' ni [[Rwanda|umunyapolitiki wo mu Rwanda]], kuri ubu akaba ari umwe mu bagize umutwe w’abadepite mu [[Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y’u Rwanda|Nteko ishinga amategeko y’u Rwanda]] . 

Ayinkamiye ahagarariye [[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|Intara y'Iburengerazuba]] kandi akomoka mu Akarere ka Rubavu. 

Kuva 2000 kugeza 2001, Ayinkamiye yari umwarimu. Kuva mu 2002 kugeza 2018, yakoraga mu myanya itandukanye mu Nteko ishinga amategeko y'u [[Rwanda]]: Umwanditsi wa Hansard (2002–2009), umwanditsi wa komite (2009–2014), n'umushinga w'amategeko (2014-2018). 

Muri Nzeri 2018, Ayinkamiye yatorewe kuba mu mutwe w'Abadepite mu Nteko ishinga amategeko y'u [[Rwanda]]. 

Ayinkamiye ari mubuyobozi bwa KCB Bank Rwanda Limited .  Ayinkamiye ari muri Komite Nyobozi y'abadepite bagize Commonwealth. 
